1
00:01:08,580 --> 00:01:09,580
I am Xie Jingchen.

2
00:01:09,660 --> 00:01:10,580
Greetings, Your Majesty.

3
00:01:10,580 --> 00:01:12,750
May I ask why you summoned Adeng and me to the palace so urgently,

4
00:01:12,750 --> 00:01:13,620
Your Majesty?

5
00:01:13,910 --> 00:01:15,240
Please rise, you three.

6
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:17,910
I have summoned you two today

7
00:01:17,910 --> 00:01:19,510
because I have a favor to ask.

8
00:01:19,580 --> 00:01:21,620
Half a month ago,

9
00:01:21,620 --> 00:01:23,250
I ordered the deposed Empress Chen to die.

10
00:01:23,250 --> 00:01:24,080
Ever since then,

11
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:25,539
the palace has been haunted every night.

12
00:01:25,539 --> 00:01:26,950
Consort Shu was so frightened

13
00:01:26,950 --> 00:01:28,120
that she went mad.

14
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:30,789
I heard you can communicate with the dead and calm their souls.

15
00:01:30,789 --> 00:01:32,200
I beg you to help me

16
00:01:32,289 --> 00:01:33,789
get rid of Chen's ghost

17
00:01:33,950 --> 00:01:35,750
and restore peace to the palace.

18
00:01:36,410 --> 00:01:38,250
Your Majesty, the ghosts are haunting us

19
00:01:38,250 --> 00:01:39,620
because their obsessions are not resolved.

20
00:01:39,620 --> 00:01:41,000
Let me go to the Cold Palace first

21
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,200
and see what happens.

22
00:01:43,660 --> 00:01:45,910
Your Majesty, I will accompany Adeng.

23
00:01:45,950 --> 00:01:47,000
The Cold Palace is full of Yin energy,

24
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:48,080
so we can look after each other.

25
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:51,410
Your Majesty, I am Adeng's accompanying physician, Qinghe.

26
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:52,450
I know medical skills

27
00:01:52,450 --> 00:01:53,910
and have prepared herbs to dispel Yin energy and soothe the nerves.

28
00:01:53,910 --> 00:01:55,620
I can also deal with the situation of Yin energy invading the body.

29
00:01:55,620 --> 00:01:57,080
Please allow me to go with them,

30
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:59,120
so I can take care of Adeng at any time.

31
00:01:59,120 --> 00:01:59,910
Granted.

32
00:02:00,580 --> 00:02:01,790
Consort Shu has been mad lately

33
00:02:01,790 --> 00:02:03,250
and often runs to the Cold Palace.

34
00:02:03,250 --> 00:02:04,910
You three must be careful.

35
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:29,160
Ah!

36
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:44,910
The resentment in this Cold Palace is too heavy.

37
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:47,000
Mugwort can stop evil spirits from entering the body.

38
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:49,079
Adeng, hold the sachet in your hand.

39
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:21,750
Ah!

40
00:03:35,250 --> 00:03:37,660
Adeng, take the medicine quickly.

41
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:48,579
Adeng, I'll be with you whatever you want to do.

42
00:03:49,540 --> 00:03:52,250
We will help her avenge her grievance.

43
00:03:53,329 --> 00:03:56,250
Yes, just looking at the resentment,

44
00:03:56,410 --> 00:03:57,660
she must have been wronged greatly,

45
00:03:57,660 --> 00:03:59,450
so she couldn't rest in peace.

46
00:04:00,790 --> 00:04:02,250
Through hell and high water,

47
00:04:02,250 --> 00:04:04,160
General Xie and I will go with you.

48
00:04:29,750 --> 00:04:31,150
His Majesty has decreed.

49
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:33,080
This is a ghost.

50
00:04:33,330 --> 00:04:35,620
The woman with the lantern is the demon's accomplice.

51
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:37,450
Burn them both to death

52
00:04:37,580 --> 00:04:38,980
to avoid future trouble.

53
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:42,610
Let's see who dares to move!

54
00:04:47,080 --> 00:04:48,450
Reporting to my master,

55
00:04:48,909 --> 00:04:50,440
the fish has taken the bait.

56
00:04:52,409 --> 00:04:57,620
They won't be able to escape this time.

57
00:04:59,790 --> 00:05:01,410
Why are you afraid of him?

58
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,400
His Majesty has decreed.

59
00:05:03,750 --> 00:05:05,000
Kill them,

60
00:05:05,540 --> 00:05:07,270
and everyone will be rewarded.

61
00:05:07,660 --> 00:05:09,000
Take one more step,

62
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:11,030
and you'll be killed.

63
00:05:17,370 --> 00:05:18,330
I see.

64
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:24,000
You're just a pawn in the Emperor's hand.

65
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:27,400
What he wants is not the peace of the palace,

66
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:30,330
but this soul lantern in my hand.

67
00:05:30,450 --> 00:05:33,620
You think burning me to death will make you Empress,

68
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:36,700
but you don't know that

69
00:05:37,159 --> 00:05:39,830
you'll be the first to be silenced

70
00:05:39,830 --> 00:05:42,330
for falsifying the imperial decree.

71
00:05:45,409 --> 00:05:47,250
It was His Majesty who sent me.

72
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,750
Burn you witch to death!

73
00:05:50,330 --> 00:05:51,790
Get rid of this ghost!

74
00:05:52,330 --> 00:05:54,370
His Majesty will make me Empress.

75
00:06:26,500 --> 00:06:27,290
Ah.

76
00:06:29,660 --> 00:06:31,450
Your Highness, don't be impulsive.

77
00:06:31,450 --> 00:06:32,450
If you do,

78
00:06:32,500 --> 00:06:33,960
you'll fall into his trap,

79
00:06:34,290 --> 00:06:35,540
and your efforts will be wasted.

80
00:06:35,540 --> 00:06:36,330
How dare you!

81
00:06:36,870 --> 00:06:38,330
Consort Shu has gone mad.

82
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:40,760
How dare she trespass in the Cold Palace?

83
00:06:44,500 --> 00:06:45,500
Miss A-Deng,

84
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:47,080
I'm sorry you were frightened.

85
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,000
Consort Shu is mad

86
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,000
and speaks nonsense.

87
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,659
It was definitely not my order.

88
00:06:50,659 --> 00:06:53,540
Why are you still putting on an act, Your Majesty?

89
00:06:54,659 --> 00:06:56,260
You invited me to the palace,

90
00:06:56,370 --> 00:06:59,570
but it was never to exorcise ghosts and calm souls, was it?

91
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:36,659
Long live the Emperor,

92
00:07:36,659 --> 00:07:40,000
long live, long, long live.

93
00:07:43,909 --> 00:07:44,700
Hmph.

94
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:53,500
Your Majesty, they are all framed.

95
00:07:53,870 --> 00:07:56,580
Please investigate this matter.

96
00:07:57,870 --> 00:07:59,580
Imperial doctor! Imperial doctor!

97
00:07:59,580 --> 00:08:00,750
Please open the door.

98
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:01,660
Please.

99
00:08:12,500 --> 00:08:13,580
By the grace of Heaven,

100
00:08:13,580 --> 00:08:14,660
the Emperor decrees.

101
00:08:14,660 --> 00:08:16,500
The deposed Empress Chen has committed treason.

102
00:08:16,500 --> 00:08:17,540
She is granted a cup of poisoned wine

103
00:08:17,540 --> 00:08:18,750
to die immediately.

104
00:08:18,870 --> 00:08:20,500
My Chen family is full of loyal subjects.

105
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:21,580
We have served the country for generations,

106
00:08:21,580 --> 00:08:24,580
risking our lives to help you conquer this vast empire,

107
00:08:24,580 --> 00:08:28,290
only to end up like this. Hahaha!
